(1) The court must seal(GL)the following documents on issue -(a) the claim form; and(b) any other document which a rule or practice direction requires it to seal.(2) The court may place the seal on the document by hand, by printing or electronically.(3) A document appearing to bear the court's seal(GL)shall be admissible in evidence without further proof.

