This practice direction supplements Part 57

CONTENTS OF THIS PRACTICE DIRECTION

Title

Paragraph number

Claim for guardianship order - rule 57.27

Para. 1

Applications

Para. 2

Giving of Notice - rule 57.29(1)(a) and rule 57.30

Para. 3

Advertisement of claim for a guardianship order or an application for a revocation/variation order - rule 57.29(1)(b)

Para. 4

Interveners - rule 57.31

Para. 5

Case management of claim for guardianship order and applications

Para. 6

OMITTED

Para. 7

Practice Direction 23 A (Applications)

Para. 8

Public Guardian to be supplied with court documents relevant to supervision of guardians

Para. 9

